step_ordered_failure_tot_s_net_handlers_eq_ind : 
forall net net' : ordered_network, 
forall failed failed' : list name, 
forall tr tr' : list (name * (input + output)), 
step_ordered_failure_star step_ordered_failure_init (failed, net) tr -> 
onwState net me = onwState net' me \/ 
(exists tr'', step_s (tot_s_map_data (onwState net me)) (tot_s_map_data (onwState net' me)) tr'').
Proof.
  intros net net' failed failed' tr tr'.
  unfold step_ordered_failure_star, step_ordered_failure_init in *.
  generalize dependent net'; generalize dependent failed'; generalize dependent tr'.
  induction H; intros; inv H0; inv H1; inv H2.
  - left. apply eq_onwState. auto.
  - right. exists tr''. apply SST_deliver; eauto.
    rewrite tot_s_map_data_apply. auto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
  - inv H. inv H0. inv H1. 
    eapply IHH; eauto.
Qed.
